title: LFM d4+ preferable
body: Looking for a adc, top and support for open league, preferably Diamond 4 or above, currently have a diamond 4 mid laner and a master tier jungler, add aL Masimo100 or post below if you are interested in trialing :)

replies.body: ADC main d5. interested in trialing for the team. just posting here for future reference. let me know if I can trial or not. look forward to hearing from you :)
